        "description": "CREATE, DESIGN, FURNISH AND DECORATE YOUR HOME EASILY IN VR AND SHARE IT WITH THE COMMUNITY!\n\nIf you want to decorate, design or create the home of your dreams, Home Design 3D VR is the perfect app for you!\n\nMAJOR UPDATE FOR MAXIMUM ACCURACY:\n· A brand new drafting interface for more accurately drawing your project\n· Real-time display of the measurements of your walls and objects\n· An advanced resizing system to set the exact dimensions of each piece of furniture and object in your project\n· Full compatibility with metric and imperial system!\n· A more comfortable user experience: vignetting, progressive movement, and so much more!\n\nIMAGINE YOUR INTERIOR AND VISIT YOUR HOME IN VR:\n\n1- Draw your plans\n· In Architect mode, choose the height of your walls, draw your floor plan, your rooms, and partitions. Add doors and windows!\n\n2- Furnish and decorate\n· Choose from over a thousand pieces of furniture and accessories, each customizable, resizable, and repositionable!\n\n3- Visit and share. Thanks to Mixed Reality, place your furniture directly in your environment!\n· Share your creations and discover those of an active community of users!\n· Invite your friends with the multi-user mode (up to 5 simultaneous online users)",
